  <brief_title>New Antibiotic to Treat Pediatric Patients With Infections Due to a Specific Bacteria (Vancomycin-Resistant Enterococcus)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Linezolid IV/PO for the Treatment of Vancomycin-Resistant Enterococcus Infections in Children</official_title>
